---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Servicios">

  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center bg-black overflow-hidden pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581094794329-cd136ce4dad5?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
        alt="Ingeniería y Construcción" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-inconed-black via-black/40 to-transparent" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold tracking-[0.2em] md:tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-sm md:text-base mb-4 block animate-fade-up">
        Catálogo de Soluciones
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-oswald text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-white leading-tight animate-fade-up-delay">
        EXPERTOS EN <br/> <span class="text-inconed-gold">CADA DETALLE</span>
      </h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-oswald text-3xl md:text-4xl text-inconed-dark mb-6">
        ARQUITECTURA, INGENIERÍA Y GESTIÓN <span class="text-inconed-gold">EN UN SOLO LUGAR</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-relaxed font-sans">
        En INCONED S.A.S. eliminamos la fragmentación. No necesitas contratar un arquitecto por un lado, un ingeniero por otro y un gestor de trámites aparte. Nosotros centralizamos todo el proceso para garantizar coherencia, ahorro y calidad.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

{/* SECCIÓN: METODOLOGÍA (Fondo Claro - Sin línea superior) */}
  <section class="py-24 bg-gray-50 relative">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
      
      {/* Encabezado */}
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-6">
        <div>
           <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm">Transparencia Total</span>
           <h2 class="font-oswald text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-2 leading-tight text-inconed-dark">
             NUESTRO PROCESO <br/><span class="text-inconed-gold">DE TRABAJO</span>
           </h2>
        </div>
        {/* Línea decorativa lateral (solo estética interna) */}
        <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-inconed-gold rounded-full md:mb-4 hidden md:block"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        
        {/* CARD 01 */}
        <div class="group relative h-[500px] shadow-2xl border-b-4 border-inconed-gold hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500">
          <img 
            src="/assets/metodologia-1.jpg" 
            alt="Análisis Técnico" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/40 to-transparent opacity-90"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute inset-0 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
            <span class="text-8xl font-oswald font-bold text-white/10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold/30 transition-colors duration-500 absolute top-4 right-4">01</span>
            
            <h3 class="font-oswald text-3xl text-white mb-3 relative z-10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold transition-colors">ANÁLISIS</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-inconed-gold pl-4 relative z-10">
              Revisión técnica detallada de tus planos para garantizar precisión antes de construir.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* CARD 02 */}
        <div class="group relative h-[500px] shadow-2xl border-b-4 border-inconed-gold hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500">
          <img 
            src="/assets/metodologia-2.jpg" 
            alt="Asesoría Experta" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/40 to-transparent opacity-90"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute inset-0 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
            <span class="text-8xl font-oswald font-bold text-white/10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold/30 transition-colors duration-500 absolute top-4 right-4">02</span>
            
            <h3 class="font-oswald text-3xl text-white mb-3 relative z-10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold transition-colors">ASESORÍA</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-inconed-gold pl-4 relative z-10">
               Guiamos tus decisiones para optimizar presupuesto sin sacrificar calidad.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* CARD 03 */}
        <div class="group relative h-[500px] shadow-2xl border-b-4 border-inconed-gold hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-500">
          <img 
            src="/assets/metodologia-3.jpg" 
            alt="Colaboración Total" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black via-black/40 to-transparent opacity-90"></div>
          
          <div class="absolute inset-0 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end">
            <span class="text-8xl font-oswald font-bold text-white/10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold/30 transition-colors duration-500 absolute top-4 right-4">03</span>
            
            <h3 class="font-oswald text-3xl text-white mb-3 relative z-10 group-hover:text-inconed-gold transition-colors">COLABORACIÓN</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-200 text-sm leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-inconed-gold pl-4 relative z-10">
              Trabajo conjunto contigo. Tu visión respaldada por nuestra experiencia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* TÍTULO PUENTE: Conecta con la siguiente sección */}
  <section class="bg-white pt-20 pb-10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm">Soluciones Integrales</span>
        <h2 class="font-oswald text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-inconed-dark mt-2 mb-6">
          NUESTROS <span class="text-inconed-gold">SERVICIOS</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gray-200 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="pb-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl space-y-24">

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="relative h-[400px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-inconed-gold/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div>
           <img 
            src="https://www.emagister.com/i/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/GettyImages-1398135990.jpg" 
            alt="Diseño Arquitectónico" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
           />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
             <div class="p-3 bg-inconed-black text-inconed-gold rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.53 16.122a3 3 0 00-5.78 1.128 2.25 2.25 0 01-2.4 2.245 4.5 4.5 0 008.4-2.245c0-.399-.078-.78-.22-1.128zm0 0a15.998 15.998 0 003.388-1.62m-5.043-.025a15.994 15.994 0 011.622-3.395m3.42 3.42a15.995 15.995 0 004.764-4.648l3.876-5.814a1.151 1.151 0 00-1.597-1.597L14.146 6.32a15.996 15.996 0 00-4.649 4.763m3.42 3.42a6.776 6.776 0 00-3.42-3.42" /></svg>
             </div>
             <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Fase 01</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-oswald text-4xl font-bold text-inconed-dark mb-6">DISEÑO ARQUITECTÓNICO</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Creamos proyectos únicos que reflejan tu identidad. Desde el boceto inicial hasta los planos constructivos detallados, nos aseguramos de que cada espacio sea funcional, estético y cumpla con las normativas vigentes.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Anteproyectos y Diseño Conceptual</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Planos Arquitectónicos y Estructurales</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Modelado BIM</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
             <div class="p-3 bg-inconed-black text-inconed-gold rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0021 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 11-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 004.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 01-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437l1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z" /></svg>
             </div>
             <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Fase 02</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-oswald text-4xl font-bold text-inconed-dark mb-6">CONSTRUCCIÓN CIVIL</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Materializamos los planos con precisión milimétrica. Contamos con equipos de trabajo calificados para ejecutar obra gris y acabados de primera, garantizando la seguridad estructural y el cumplimiento de cronogramas.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Dirección Técnica de Obra</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Estructuras de Hormigón y Acero</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Instalaciones Hidrosanitarias y Eléctricas</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative h-[400px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-inconed-gold/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div>
           <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200" 
            alt="Construcción Civil" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
           />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="relative h-[400px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-inconed-gold/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div>
           <img 
            src="https://www.kin.energy/PAgina%20KINENERGY%20IMAGENES/Imagenes%20Blog/Art%C3%ADculos%202022/Dise%C3%B1o-de-ingenier%C3%ADas-el%C3%A9ctrico-hidrosanitarias-PCI-HVAC.png" 
            alt="Remodelación" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
           />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
             <div class="p-3 bg-inconed-black text-inconed-gold rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.5 12c0-1.232-.046-2.453-.138-3.662a4.006 4.006 0 00-3.7-3.7 48.678 48.678 0 00-7.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 00-3.7 3.7c-.017.22-.032.441-.046.662M19.5 12l3-3m-3 3l-3-3m-12 3c0 1.232.046 2.453.138 3.662a4.006 4.006 0 003.7 3.7 48.656 48.656 0 007.324 0 4.006 4.006 0 003.7-3.7c.017-.22.032-.441.046-.662M4.5 12l3 3m-3-3l-3 3" /></svg>
             </div>
             <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Transformación</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-oswald text-4xl font-bold text-inconed-dark mb-6">REMODELACIÓN</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Damos nueva vida a espacios antiguos. Ya sea una vivienda, una oficina o un local comercial, modernizamos tus ambientes optimizando la distribución y mejorando la iluminación y ventilación.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Ampliaciones y Reformas</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Cambio de Acabados (Pisos, Paredes)</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Mantenimiento Preventivo</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center group">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
             <div class="p-3 bg-inconed-black text-inconed-gold rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" /></svg>
             </div>
             <span class="text-inconed-gold font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Gestión Legal</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-oswald text-4xl font-bold text-inconed-dark mb-6">TRÁMITES MUNICIPALES</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Olvídate de las filas y la burocracia. Nuestro equipo legal y técnico gestiona todos los permisos necesarios ante el GAD Municipal para que tu obra sea 100% legal y segura.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Permisos de Construcción</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Propiedad Horizontal y Subdivisiones</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-700"><span class="text-inconed-gold">✔</span> Regularización de Edificaciones</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 relative h-[400px] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-inconed-gold/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-500 z-10"></div>
           <img 
            src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-photo/young-business-man-suit-is-managing-paperwork-office-many-paperwork-that-is-finished-documents-company-about-finance-information-company_208349-1013.jpg" 
            alt="Trámites Municipales" 
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700"
           />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
      <h2 class="font-oswald text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">SERVICIOS COMPLEMENTARIOS</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex items-start gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
           <div class="p-4 bg-inconed-dark text-white rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20.25 7.5l-.625 10.632a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.247 2.118H6.622a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.247-2.118L3.75 7.5M10 11.25h4M3.375 7.5h17.25c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H3.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z" /></svg>
           </div>
           <div>
              <h3 class="font-oswald text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Diseño de Interiores</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Selección de mobiliario, diseño de iluminación, paleta de colores y texturas para crear ambientes confortables.</p>
           </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex items-start gap-6 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
           <div class="p-4 bg-inconed-dark text-white rounded-full">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21 7.5l-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0l-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9" /></svg>
           </div>
           <div>
              <h3 class="font-oswald text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Visualización 3D</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Recorridos virtuales y renders de alta definición para que visualices tu inversión antes de poner el primer ladrillo.</p>
           </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-inconed-gold text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="font-oswald text-4xl font-bold text-black mb-6">¿NECESITAS ASESORÍA TÉCNICA?</h2>
      <a href="https://wa.me/593994218531" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-black text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl hover:scale-105">
        Solicitar Presupuesto
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>